00:17:53,615 --> 00:17:55,795
冰海将融
The sea ice begins to melt.

196
00:17:57,895 --> 00:17:59,665
待到浮冰融化之时
And as it breaks apart,

197
00:17:59,665 --> 00:18:02,605
一年一度的夏季迁徙就开始了
it triggers an annual summer migration.

