00:18:12,535 --> 00:18:15,905
开始追随着融冰向海湾进发
follow the melting ice into the bays and fjords.

200
00:18:19,125 --> 00:18:23,485
这是北极猎人们千载难逢的机会
For Arctic hunters, this creates a unique opportunity.

201
00:18:36,815 --> 00:18:38,095
马穆拉・克里斯蒂安森
Mamarut Kristiansen,

202
00:18:38,095 --> 00:18:40,335
